text:
Great job today, Hinana. We have some time,
do you want to get something to eat?

Alright, it's decided then.
Is there something you want to eat?

Um~…
Hinana, wants to eat ice cream~!

Okay, got it.
────Ah, isn’t that an ice cream shop over there?

That shop…
If I remember right, they have dozens of flavors…

Yeah, that's right~
Hinana will have the nuts and caramel one~

You’ve already decided…
Hmm… What should I get…

…Then, Hinana will choose for you~ Hinana will pick my
favorite flavor… and you’ll give me a bite, okay~♡
